Pantheon Canonical Doctrine

Semantic Volume Engine (SVE)

Purpose

Represent, compress, translate, preserve, and reconstruct meaning by operating on semantic invariants rather than surface symbols.

⸻

Core Axiom

Symbols are shadows. Meaning is the latent structure capable of generating many equivalent symbolic forms.

Pantheon therefore optimizes for preserving generative structure, not literal wording.

